==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Traduct
<hw>Tra*duct"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>traducere</ets>, <ets>traductum</ets>. See Traduce.]</ety> <def>To
derive or deduce; also, to transmit; to transfer.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Fotherby.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traduct</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Traduct
<hw>Tra*duct"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which is traducted; that
which is transferred; a translation.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traduction</ent>⟦br⟧
